	<body>

		<section name="Issue Tracking">

			<p>
				HAPI uses Sourceforge to track issues and feature requests.	
			</p>
			
			<p>
				To submit a ticket with regards to a problem, bug, or defect with
				HAPI, please see the
				<a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/hl7api/bugs/">bugs tracker</a>.
				When submitting a new issue ticket, please try to include as much
				details as you can. Sample messages, code reproducing the issue, etc
				are all very useful and help us to fix the issue.
			</p>
			
			<p>
				To submit a request for a new feature or enhancement, please use
				the
				<a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/hl7api/feature-requests/">feature requests tracker</a>.
			</p>
			
		</section>


	</body>
